x, and t_RH as a function of r, f, and g_\\ast (and to a weaker extent\nthe particle content of the vacuum near the Planck epoch).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Dec 2005 17:46:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Jun 2006 15:23:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
